snippet.title: The Sims 3 University Life Producer Walkthrough
snippet.description: Check out the wild parties, chaotic class schedules, new activities, and crazy hijinks in The Sims 3 University Life expansion pack! Learn about new university venues including campus dorms, favorite local hangouts, and party hot spots! Plus, get a sneak peek of how your Sims can use their new smartphones to text, blog, check their social group status, take photos, and more. The Sims 3 University Life Expansion Pack is available March 5, 2013!
